==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sweepwasher
<hw>Sweep"wash`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who extracts
the residuum of precious metals from the sweepings, potsherds, etc., of
refineries of gold and silver, or places where these metals are
used.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sweepy</ent>⟦br⟧
